{"tid":1644551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人無恥便無敵 ! 可恥！","createTime":"2019-10-10T14:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T15:12:00.000Z","uid":270568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3bca0fef1b060a6b6aafd5cfd4a40486358bb125","tid":1644551,"uid":270568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/columns/15/20191010/802487/專欄-幸福摩天輪-天使\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fcolumns%2F15%2F20191010%2F802487%2F%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F%E6%91%A9%E5%A4%A9%E8%BC%AA-%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5YgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=da7d0a65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fcolumns%2F15%2F20191010%2F802487%2F%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F%E6%91%A9%E5%A4%A9%E8%BC%AA-%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF&h=efce83f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/columns/15/20191010/802487/專欄-幸福摩天輪-天使</a><br />\n<br />\n﻿幸福摩天輪&mdash;&mdash;「天使」<br />\n幸福摩天輪 2019-10-10 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n朋友傳來一段「三級」影片，據說是自動獻身的「天使」，只見一個戴着黑口罩的年輕裸女，和另一個男人性交，身旁另有兩個裸女候命，一個旁觀，一個碌手機，若無其事。在性交的女生木無表情，動作機械。三個裸女身體未完全發育，年輕得令人難過。畫外音是一把成熟男聲，以「天使」作餌，召募「前線兄弟」。又說「知道大家辛苦，可以contact我。」還喊了一句「光復香港！」全是現場收音。現場設備簡陋，像一間軍妓工廠。<br />\n<br />\n　　在追查天使騙局時，朋友再傳來某名校女生和某男生性交的照片，據說她也是獻身的天使！朋友說，有一個真人真事個案，「天使」本是讀著名女校的乖乖女。初時，她不願去參加暴亂，但師姐叫她，她不好意思推掉。在暴亂現場認識了男的勇武派，暴亂完了大家去飲酒，瞬間變成了廢青的洩慾工具。後被家人發現，但女生不覺有問題。家人把她送走，離開香港，斬斷罪惡根源。<br />\n<br />\n　　早在九月初，羅范椒芬曾揭發有少女被誘騙，向暴徒提供免費性愛，被稱為「天使」。後來，一個十四歲「天使」背向鏡頭接受訪問，講述被引誘以致懷孕被迫流產的悲慘故事。九月二十二日，警員在青馬收費廣場截查時，在一名黑衣暴徒身上搜出一張假記者證、多個避孕套及一支潤滑劑，疑有人欲趁亂局，假冒記者欺騙無知少女獻身。可見「天使」騙局並非空穴來風。<br />\n<br />\n　　當爛頭卒自我催眠是義士，無知少女被誘騙做「天使」。美好的青春被糟蹋，叫人痛心！看似高尚的革命，和拳頭、枕頭及銀頭，糾纏不清。<br />\n<br />\n潘麗瓊"},{"pid":"b234b92f4aac76523dcb99e055c99664926f26a1","tid":1644551,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"屌，咩人黎<br />\n咁都寫得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56c4032ea25a3961944fee57393ebacb219b49b","tid":1644551,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"創意台"},{"pid":"35f1985654b533be7c0e81d07f6997e107cebbf4","tid":1644551,"uid":270568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b234b92f4aac76523dcb99e055c99664926f26a1","tid":1644551,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"屌，咩人黎<br />\n咁都寫得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"好 L過份！仆街文妓等天修！！！"}]}